# Copy this to .env.local and fill in real values. .env.local is gitignored.
#
# Google Maps JavaScript API key — required by /terminal-map for the live
# walking-directions view. Restrict the key in Google Cloud Console:
#   - Application restriction: HTTP referrers
#   - API restriction: Maps JavaScript API + Directions API + Map Tiles API
# Without a key, /terminal-map falls back to a "needs configuration" notice.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
